h4. Actor:
Director, Project Director, Chief Financial Officer.

h4. Description:
This is the landing page of *Sprint Budget* with input form on top and grid view at the bottom.

h4. Flow: 
* Actor clicks [Budget|guide:renderBudgetMenu] option from top menu bar.
* "Budget" sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click "Sprint" link
* Show Landing Page of ["Sprint Budget"|guide:ShowBudgSprintActionService].

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Show sprint budget" privilege.

h4. Process:
* [Get List of all "Budget Sprint" from server|guide:ListSprintBudgetActionService].

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show "Sprint Budget" of landing page.
** Show input form on top.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].